{{Infobox book | name = Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom, and Normativity | author = [[Sacha Golob]] | image = | subject = [[Heidegger]]'s philosophy | published = 2014 | publisher = [[Cambridge University Press]] | pages = 282 pp. | isbn = 9781107031708 }} '''''Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom, and Normativity''''' is a 2014 book by [[Sacha Golob]], in which the author provides an account of the arguments and concepts characterizing [[Heidegger]]'s early thought and examines their positions both in contemporary [[analytic philosophy]] and the [[history of philosophy]]. He argues against existing interpretations of Heidegger on [[intentionality]] and believes that Heidegger emphasizes a unique position regarding conceptual and representational content.<ref>{{cite journal |last1=McKinney |first1=Tucker |title=Heidegger on concepts, freedom, and normativity, by SachaGolob. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 2014, xvii + 272 pp. ISBN 13: 978-1107031708 hb £62.00; ISBN 13: 978-1316631904 pb £23.99 |journal=[[European Journal of Philosophy]] |date=December 2017 |volume=25 |issue=4 |pages=1232–1235 |doi=10.1111/ejop.12309 |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/ejop.12309 |accessdate=26 November 2018 |language=en |issn=0966-8373}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Crowell |first1=Steven |title=Review: Sacha Golub . Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom, and Normativity . |journal=[[Philosophy in Review]] |date=April 2015 |volume=XXXV |issue=2 |url=https://journals.uvic.ca/index.php/pir/article/viewFile/13522/4378 |accessdate=26 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Campbell |first1=Scott M. |title=Review of Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom and Normativity |journal=Notre Dame Philosophical Reviews |date=18 August 2016 |url=https://ndpr.nd.edu/news/heidegger-on-concepts-freedom-and-normativity/ |accessdate=26 November 2018 |issn=1538-1617}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Cregan |first1=Joseph |title=Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom and Normativity |journal=[[International Journal of Philosophical Studies]] |date=8 August 2015 |volume=23 |issue=4 |pages=599–604 |doi=10.1080/09672559.2015.1077584 |url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/09672559.2015.1077584?src=recsys&journalCode=riph20 |accessdate=26 November 2018 |language=en |issn=0967-2559}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Keiling |first1=Tobias |title=Review: Heidegger on Concepts, Freedom, and Normativity|url=https://kclpure.kcl.ac.uk/portal/files/97578139/Reviews_of_Heidegger_Concepts_Normativity_Golob_CUP.pdf|journal=Zeitschrift für philosophische Forschung |date=2016 |pages=19-21}}</ref>
